OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779188576
OL,3,COfcom's push to tackle intimate image
OL,4,Cabuse falls short, survivors say
OL,6,FSurvivors of online sexual abuse told
OL,7,FITV News Correspondent Sejal Karia
OL,8,Fthat new guidance aimed at forcing
OL,9,Fplatforms to do more doesn't go far
OL,10,Fenough
OL,12,FThis report contains details of online
OL,13,Fabuse which you may find upsetting
OL,15,FOfcom has announced new measures aimed
OL,16,Fat tackling the spread of intimate
OL,17,Fimages shared without consent online,
OL,18,Fincluding sexualised deepfakes and
OL,19,Fvideos of women being raped while
OL,20,Funconscious.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
