CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779188576
OL,3,COfcom's push to tackle intimate image
OL,4,Cabuse falls short, survivors say
OL,6,FThe regulator says its guidance will
OL,7,Fpush tech companies to do more to
OL,8,Fdetect and remove abusive content
OL,9,Facross multiple platforms.
OL,11,FBut survivors say the burden still
OL,12,Ffalls on survivors to search the
OL,13,Finternet for evidence of their own
OL,14,Fabuse.
OL,16,FZoe and Amanda were both raped by
OL,17,Ftheir partners while unconscious. They
OL,18,Fsay images of the abuse were taken
OL,19,Fwithout their knowledge
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779188576
OL,3,COfcom's push to tackle intimate image
OL,4,Cabuse falls short, survivors say
OL,6,F"This is the ultimate betrayal,"
OL,7,FAmanda said. "It's being drugged, it's
OL,8,Fbeing raped and it's being shown to
OL,9,Fthe world for other people to see."
OL,11,FBoth women say Ofcom's latest
OL,12,Frecommendations are a step forward `
OL,13,Fbut do not go nearly far enough,
OL,14,Fespecially for women who may not even
OL,15,Fknow they are victims.
OL,17,FAmanda said she does not trust
OL,18,Fwebsites to remove abusive content
OL,19,Fvoluntarily.
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@`O]oD@NOUqD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779188576
OL,3,COfcom's push to tackle intimate image
OL,4,Cabuse falls short, survivors say
OL,6,F"There's a demand." Amanda told me.
OL,7,F"And I think whilst people are
OL,8,Fsearching for it, looking for this...
OL,9,FI don't trust that people will do the
OL,10,Fright thing and the moral thing and
OL,11,Ftake this content down."
OL,13,FZoe said many women are now left
OL,14,Fsearching the internet for evidence of
OL,15,Ftheir own abuse.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779188576
OL,3,COfcom's push to tackle intimate image
OL,4,Cabuse falls short, survivors say
OL,6,F"I recognise that it is a start, but
OL,7,Fit doesn't cover women that have
OL,8,Fexperienced a drug facilitated rape,"
OL,9,Fshe said. "We are liaising with lots
OL,10,Fof women that are coming from a point
OL,11,Fof hindsight where they think 'I need
OL,12,Fto start trawling the internet for
OL,13,Fpictures of me'."
OL,15,F"I believe the responsibility needs to
OL,16,Fbe on the sites and the moderators,"
OL,17,Fshe added.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
