OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779188576
OL,3,COfcom's push to tackle intimate image
OL,4,Cabuse falls short, survivors say
OL,6,FThe images and videos are often easy
OL,7,Fto find online within seconds. ITV
OL,8,FNews is not naming the platforms
OL,9,Fhosting the material.
OL,11,FOfcom says under its new guidance,
OL,12,Fvictims would only need to report an
OL,13,Fimage once through services like
OL,14,FStopNCII.org, which creates a digital
OL,15,F"hash" ` a unique fingerprint allowing
OL,16,Fmatching images to be identified and
OL,17,Fremoved across multiple platforms
OL,18,Fautomatically.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
