OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779188576
OL,3,COfcom's push to tackle intimate image
OL,4,Cabuse falls short, survivors say
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News, Ofcom
OL,7,Facknowledged survivors have carried
OL,8,Fthe burden of reporting abuse for too
OL,9,Flong.
OL,11,F"What this recommendation does is say
OL,12,Fyou need to report it once," Jess
OL,13,FSmith, Ofcom's Principal for Online
OL,14,FSafety said. "That hash can then be
OL,15,Fshared with every site in scope of the
OL,16,Frecommendation, so victims and
OL,17,Fsurvivors don't have to do the work of
OL,18,Ftrawling the internet."
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@\O]vD@NOUzD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
