OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779188576
OL,3,COfcom's push to tackle intimate image
OL,4,Cabuse falls short, survivors say
OL,6,FBut when challenged on the millions of
OL,7,Fabusive images still circulating
OL,8,Fonline, Ofcom admitted compliance from
OL,9,Ftech companies is "not where we would
OL,10,Fwant it to be".
OL,12,FFor survivors, the process of
OL,13,Freporting abuse can itself become
OL,14,Fdeeply distressing.
OL,16,F"All of this is trauma to a survivor,"
OL,17,FAmanda said.
OL,26,@qD@SOUrD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779188576
OL,3,COfcom's push to tackle intimate image
OL,4,Cabuse falls short, survivors say
OL,6,F"They're likely going through a police
OL,7,Finvestigation, which is trauma. They
OL,8,Fhave these images out there, which is
OL,9,Ftrauma.
OL,11,F"They have PTSD and then they're
OL,12,Fexpected to find images of themselves
OL,13,Fand then if anything is found of you,
OL,14,Fit will start off an investigation.
OL,16,F"So another prolonged process of
OL,17,Ftrying to get this video or images
OL,18,Fremoved and then investigated. It's
OL,19,Fjust awful.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
