OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779188576
OL,3,COfcom's push to tackle intimate image
OL,4,Cabuse falls short, survivors say
OL,6,FIf you want to make contact with our
OL,7,Fteam, please email
OL,8,Finvestigations@itv.com
OL,10,FCampaigners warn image-based abuse is
OL,11,Frapidly increasing, fuelled by AI and
OL,12,Fdeepfake technology and until
OL,13,Fplatforms are forced to stop this
OL,14,Fmaterial appearing online in the first
OL,15,Fplace, the burden will continue to
OL,16,Ffall on the women living with the
OL,17,Fconsequences.
OL,19,FWe approached a number of technology
OL,20,Fcompanies for a response to Ofcom's
OL,21,Fmeasures.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779188576
OL,3,COfcom's push to tackle intimate image
OL,4,Cabuse falls short, survivors say
OL,6,FMicrosoft said it "supports a holistic
OL,7,Fapproach to tackle non-consensual
OL,8,Fintimate imagery and has proactively
OL,9,Fused hash-matching to reduce harm to
OL,10,Fvictims.
OL,12,F"We welcome Ofcom's goal of
OL,13,Fencouraging the use of proactive
OL,14,Fmeasures, but it's important the
OL,15,Fframework remains clear,
OL,16,Fproportionate, and flexible - so it
OL,17,Fsupports innovation, respects rights,
OL,18,Fand maintains public trust."
OL,26,@zD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
