OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779188576
OL,3,COfcom's push to tackle intimate image
OL,4,Cabuse falls short, survivors say
OL,6,FGoogle said: "It is committed to
OL,7,Fpreventing and addressing the distress
OL,8,Fand harm caused by non-consensual
OL,9,Fintimate imagery.
OL,11,FOver the years, we have invested
OL,12,Fdeeply in industry-leading
OL,13,Fprotections, including hash matching.
OL,15,F"Tackling this issue requires
OL,16,Fcontinuous work, and our approach is
OL,17,Fconstantly evolving, informed by
OL,18,Fvictim-survivors and experts."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
